UIDescription.NativeString: Group up and outlast all of the other squads gunning for victory.

A team deathmatch with four teams of eight. The first to 200 points wins.

Hop in your trusty vehicle with the squad and gear up to fight in a big city arena.

Only one team can emerge the winner amongst the chaos!

Tags: team deathmatch, squad

Original Map Name: Red/Green/Yellow/Purple - Car Fight

Zone Wars Purgatory is the first of it's kind. This LTM offers players unending gameplay with activities like Box Fights or Parkour to keep you entertained when eliminated early.

Queue up solo and battle it out in high action Zone Wars! You will be automatically matched with other players to fill a lobby.

This is a hub with access to some of the hottest new vehicles games in Creative. 

Check back daily for the latest updates and newest maps.

Tags: race, arcade

Original Map Name: Best Vehicles Games in Creative
Classic Battle Royale with Three-Person Squads.

Monsters have taken over the city! Earn gold by clearing them out.

Make sure to stop by the shop to upgrade your gear. If you look around you can even find loot.

Team up with others or survive on your own in this open world city.

Tags: open world, survival, creatures, role playing

Original Map Name: Outbreak

Welcome to Tiny Town, a place to hang out with friends and roleplay.

Work cool jobs, earn money, buy your own amazing house, and play fun mini-games.

There’s no win condition in Tiny Town. You play to have fun!

Tags: economy, peaceful, role playing, shop

Original Map Name: PWR Tiny Town
